11#include "modules/video_coding/event_wrapper.h"
12
13#include "rtc_base/event.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17class EventWrapperImpl : public EventWrapper {
18 public:
19 ~EventWrapperImpl() override {}
20
21 bool Set() override {
22 event_.Set();
23 return true;
24 }
25
26 EventTypeWrapper Wait(int max_time_ms) override {
27 return event_.Wait(max_time_ms) ? kEventSignaled : kEventTimeout;
28 }
29
30 private:
31 rtc::Event event_;
32};
33
34// static
35EventWrapper* EventWrapper::Create() {
36 return new EventWrapperImpl();
37}
38
39} // namespace webrtc
